public int luckySum(int a, int b, int c)                                                            public int luckySum(int a, int b, int c)                                                            
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
	int sum = a+b+c;                                                                                   	int sum = a+b+c;                                                                                   
    if (a == 13)                                                                                        if (a == 13)                                                                                    
        return 0;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
    if (b==13)                                                                                          if (b==13)                                                                                      
        return a;                                                                                           return a;                                                                                   
    if (c==0)                                                                                           if (c==13)                                                                                      
        return a+b;                                                                                         return a+b;                                                                                 
    else return sum;                                                                                    else return sum;                                                                                
}                                                                                                   }

public int luckySum(int a, int b, int c)                                                            public int luckySum(int a, int b, int c)                                                            
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	int sum = a+b+c;                                                                                   	int sum = a+b+c;                                                                                   
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	if (a == 13)                                                                                       	if (a == 13)                                                                                       
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	return 0;                                                                                          	return 0;                                                                                          
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	if (b==13)                                                                                         	if (b==13)                                                                                         
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	return a;                                                                                          	return a;                                                                                          
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	if (c==13)                                                                                         	if (c==13)                                                                                         
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	return a+b;                                                                                        	return a+b;                                                                                        
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	else                                                                                               	else                                                                                               
	return sum;                                                                                        	return sum;                                                                                        
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
}                                                                                                   }

public boolean isEverywhere(int[] nums, int val)                                                    public boolean isEverywhere(int[] nums, int val)                                                    
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    for(int i = 0; i < nums.length - 1; i++)                                                            for(int i = 0; i < nums.length - 1; i++)                                                        
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	if(nums[i] == val && nums[i+1] == val)                                                             	if(nums[i] != val && nums[i+1] != val)                                                        
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
         	return true;                                                                                       	return false;                                                                             
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return false;                                                                                       return true;                                                                                    
}                                                                                                   }

public boolean isEverywhere(int[] nums, int val)                                                    public boolean isEverywhere(int[] nums, int val)                                                    
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    for (int i = 0; i< nums.length-1;i++)                                                               for (int i = 0; i< nums.length-1;i++)                                                           
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
        if (nums[i]==val && nums[i+1]==val)                                                                 if (nums[i]!=val && nums[i+1]!=val)                                                         
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            return true;                                                                                        return false;                                                                           
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return false;                                                                                       return true;                                                                                    
}                                                                                                   }

public boolean isEverywhere(int[] nums, int val)                                                    public boolean isEverywhere(int[] nums, int val)                                                    
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    for (int i = 0; i < nums.length; i++)                                                               //if (nums.length%2 == 0)                                                                       
    {                                                                                                   for (int i = 0; i < nums.length -1; i++)                                                        
        if (nums[i] == val || nums[i+1] == val)                                                         {                                                                                               
        {                                                                                                   if (nums[i] == val || nums[i+1] == val)                                                     
                                                                                                            {                                                                                           
        }                                                                                                                                                                                               
        else                                                                                                }                                                                                           
            return false;                                                                                   else                                                                                        
    }                                                                                                           return false;                                                                           
    return true;                                                                                        }                                                                                               
}                                                                                                       return true;                                                                                    
                                                                                                    }

public boolean isEverywhere(int[] nums, int val)                                                    public boolean isEverywhere(int[] nums, int val)                                                    
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    for (int i = 0; i <= nums.length - 1; i++) {                                                        for (int i = 0; i <= nums.length - 2; i++) {                                                    
        if (nums[i] != val && nums[i+1] != val) {                                                           if (nums[i] != val && nums[i+1] != val) {                                                   
            return false;                                                                                       return false;                                                                           
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return true;                                                                                        return true;                                                                                    
}                                                                                                   }

public boolean isEverywhere(int[] nums, int val)                                                    public boolean isEverywhere(int[] nums, int val)                                                    
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	for (int i = 0;                                                                                    	for (int i = 0;                                                                                    
	i <= nums.length - 2;                                                                              	i <= nums.length - 2;                                                                              
	i++) {                                                                                             	i++) {                                                                                             
		                                                                                                  		                                                                                                  
		if (nums[i]!= val && nums[i+1]!= val) {                                                           		if (nums[i]!= val && nums[i+1]!= val) {                                                           
			                                                                                                 			                                                                                                 
			                                                                                                 			                                                                                                 
			return false;                                                                                    			return false;                                                                                    
			                                                                                                 			                                                                                                 
		}                                                                                                 		}                                                                                                 
		                                                                                                  		                                                                                                  
	}                                                                                                  	}

public int noTeenSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                           public int noTeenSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                           
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int n = 0;                                                                                          int n = 0;                                                                                      
	n = a;                                                                                             	a = n;                                                                                             
    this.fixTeen(n);                                                                                    this.fixTeen(n);                                                                                
    n = b;                                                                                              b = n;                                                                                          
    this.fixTeen(n);                                                                                    this.fixTeen(n);                                                                                
    n = c;                                                                                              c = n;                                                                                          
    this.fixTeen(n);                                                                                    this.fixTeen(n);                                                                                
    return a + b + c;                                                                                   return a + b + c;                                                                               
}                                                                                                   }                                                                                                   
public int fixTeen(int n)                                                                           public int fixTeen(int n)                                                                           
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (n > 12 && n < 20)                                                                               if (n > 12 && n < 20)                                                                           
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	n = 0;                                                                                             	n = 0;                                                                                        
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return 0;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                       
}                                                                                                   }

public int noTeenSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                           public int noTeenSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                           
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int n = 0;                                                                                          int n = 0;                                                                                      
	a = n;                                                                                             	n = a;                                                                                             
    this.fixTeen(n);                                                                                    this.fixTeen(n);                                                                                
    b = n;                                                                                              n = b;                                                                                          
    this.fixTeen(n);                                                                                    this.fixTeen(n);                                                                                
    c = n;                                                                                              n = c;                                                                                          
    this.fixTeen(n);                                                                                    this.fixTeen(n);                                                                                
    return a + b + c;                                                                                   return a + b + c;                                                                               
}                                                                                                   }                                                                                                   
public int fixTeen(int n)                                                                           public int fixTeen(int n)                                                                           
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (n > 12 && n < 20)                                                                               if ((n > 12 && n < 20) && (n != 15 || n != 16))                                                 
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	n = 0;                                                                                             	n = 0;                                                                                        
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return 0;                                                                                           return n;                                                                                       
}                                                                                                   }

     	this.fixTeen(a);                                                                              public int fixTeen(int n)

     	this.fixTeen(b);                                                                                   	return n;

     	this.fixTeen(c);                                                                                                                                                                                  
    }

public int fixTeen(int n)                                                                                                                                                                               
{                                                                                                                                                                                                       
	if (n == 15 || n == 16)                                                                                                                                                                                
    {                                                                                                                                                                                                   
     	n = n;                                                                                                                                                                                            
    }                                                                                                                                                                                                   
    else if (n >= 13 && n <= 19)                                                                                                                                                                        
    {                                                                                                                                                                                                   
     	n = 0;                                                                                                                                                                                            
    }                                                                                                                                                                                                   
    return n;

    noTeenSum=a+b+c;                                                                                    noTeenSum=a+b+c;

public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (a > 21 && b > 21) {                                                                           if (a > 21 && b > 21) {                                                                           
        return 0;                                                                                         return 0;                                                                                     
    }else if (a > 21) {                                                                               }else if (a > 21) {                                                                               
        return a;                                                                                         return b;                                                                                     
    }                                                                                                 } else if (b > 21) {                                                                              
                                                                                                          return a;                                                                                     
    int sumA = 21 - a;                                                                                }                                                                                                 
    int sumB = 21 - b;                                                                                int sumA = 21 - a;                                                                                
                                                                                                      int sumB = 21 - b;                                                                                
    if (sumA > sumB) {                                                                                if (sumA > sumB) {                                                                                
        return b;                                                                                         return b;                                                                                     
    } else {                                                                                          } else {                                                                                          
        return a;                                                                                         return a;                                                                                     
    }                                                                                                 }                                                                                                 
}                                                                                                   }

		return b;                                                                                         		return a;

    if (a > 0 && b > 0)                                                                                 if (a > 0 && b > 0)                                                                             
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	if (b > 21 && a <= 21)                                                                             	if (b > 21 && a <= 21)                                                                        
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
         	return a;                                                                                          	return a;                                                                                 
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        else if (a > 21 && b <= 21)                                                                         else if (a > b && a <= 21)                                                                  
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
         	return b;                                                                                          	return a;                                                                                 
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                       else if (a > 21 && b <= 21)                                                                 
    return 0;                                                                                               {                                                                                           
}                                                                                                            	return b;                                                                                 
                                                                                                            }

                                                                                                            {                                                                                           
                                                                                                            	return b;                                                                                  
                                                                                                            }                                                                                           
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
                                                                                                        return 0;                                                                                       
                                                                                                    }

public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (a > 21 && b > 21)                                                                               if (a > 21 && b > 21)                                                                           
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return 0;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if ((21 - a) < (21 - b))                                                                       else if (a <= 21 && b <= 21)                                                                    
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return a;                                                                                           if ((21 - a) < (21 - b))                                                                    
    }                                                                                                       {                                                                                           
    else                                                                                                        return a;                                                                               
    {                                                                                                       }                                                                                           
        return b;                                                                                           else                                                                                        
    }                                                                                                       {                                                                                           
}                                                                                                               return b;                                                                               
                                                                                                            }

                                                                                                        {                                                                                               
                                                                                                            return b;                                                                                   
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
                                                                                                        else                                                                                            
                                                                                                        {                                                                                               
                                                                                                            return a;                                                                                   
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
                                                                                                    }

public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (a > 21 && b > 21)                                                                               if (a > 21 && b > 21)                                                                           
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return 0;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if ((21 - a) < (21 - b))                                                                       else if (a <= 21 && b <= 21)                                                                    
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return a;                                                                                           if ((21 - a) < (21 - b))                                                                    
    }                                                                                                       {                                                                                           
    else                                                                                                        return a;                                                                               
    {                                                                                                       }                                                                                           
        return b;                                                                                           else                                                                                        
    }                                                                                                       {                                                                                           
}                                                                                                               return b;                                                                               
                                                                                                            }                                                                                           
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
                                                                                                        else if (a > 21)                                                                                
                                                                                                        {                                                                                               
                                                                                                            return b;                                                                                   
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
                                                                                                        else                                                                                            
                                                                                                        {                                                                                               
                                                                                                            return a;                                                                                   
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
                                                                                                    }                                                                                                   
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
---------------------------------A1+Da----------------------------------------------------------------------------A1+Db-----------------------------------------------------
public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	if (a > 21 && b > 21)                                                                              	if (a > 21 && b > 21)                                                                              
	{                                                                                                  	{                                                                                                  
		                                                                                                  		                                                                                                  
		                                                                                                  		                                                                                                  
		return 0;                                                                                         		return 0;                                                                                         
		                                                                                                  		                                                                                                  
	}                                                                                                  	}                                                                                                  
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	else if ((21 - b) > (21 - a))                                                                      	else if ((21 - b) < (21 - a))                                                                      
	{                                                                                                  	{                                                                                                  
		                                                                                                  		                                                                                                  
		                                                                                                  		                                                                                                  
		return b;                                                                                         		return b;                                                                                         
		                                                                                                  		                                                                                                  
	}                                                                                                  	}                                                                                                  
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	else                                                                                               	else if ((21 - a) > (21 - b))                                                                      
	{                                                                                                  	{                                                                                                  
		                                                                                                  		                                                                                                  
		                                                                                                  		                                                                                                  
		return a;                                                                                         		return a;                                                                                         
		                                                                                                  		                                                                                                  
	}                                                                                                  	}                                                                                                  
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
}                                                                                                   	else                                                                                               
                                                                                                    	{                                                                                                  
                                                                                                    		                                                                                                  
                                                                                                    		                                                                                                  
                                                                                                    		return a;                                                                                         
                                                                                                    		                                                                                                  
                                                                                                    	}                                                                                                  
                                                                                                    	                                                                                                   
                                                                                                    }

public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (a > 21 && b > 21)                                                                               if (a <= 21 && b <= 21)                                                                         
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return 0;                                                                                        	return Math.max(a,b);                                                                         
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    if (a > b)                                                                                          if (a <= 21)                                                                                    
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
       	return a;                                                                                        	return a;                                                                                     
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                                                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   else if (b <= 21)                                                                               
      	return b;                                                                                        {                                                                                               
    }                                                                                                    	return b;                                                                                     
}                                                                                                       }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                        else                                                                                            
                                                                                                        {                                                                                               
                                                                                                         	return 0;                                                                                     
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                        /*if (a > 21 || b > 21)                                                                         
                                                                                                        {                                                                                               
                                                                                                            return 0;                                                                                   
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
                                                                                                        if (a > b)                                                                                      
                                                                                                        {                                                                                               
                                                                                                           	return a;                                                                                   
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
                                                                                                        else                                                                                            
                                                                                                        {                                                                                               
                                                                                                          	return b;                                                                                    
                                                                                                        }*/                                                                                             
                                                                                                    }

public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if ((a>21)&&(b>21))                                                                                 if ((a>21)&&(b>21))                                                                             
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return 0;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        if(a>b)                                                                                             if(a>b && a<21)                                                                             
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            return a;                                                                                           return a;                                                                               
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        else if(b>a)                                                                                        else if(b>a && b<21)                                                                        
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            return b;                                                                                           return b;                                                                               
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
        else                                                                                                else                                                                                        
            return 0;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                               
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
}                                                                                                   }

	if ((a>21)&&(b>21))                                                                                	if ((a>21)&&(b>21))

	}                                                                                                  	}                                                                                                  
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	else                                                                                               	else                                                                                               
	{                                                                                                  	{                                                                                                  
		                                                                                                  		                                                                                                  
		if(a>b)                                                                                           		if(a>b)                                                                                           
		{                                                                                                 		{                                                                                                 
			                                                                                                 			                                                                                                 
			                                                                                                 			                                                                                                 
			return a;                                                                                        			return a;                                                                                        
			                                                                                                 			                                                                                                 
		}                                                                                                 		}                                                                                                 
		                                                                                                  		                                                                                                  
		else if(b>a)                                                                                      		else if(b>a)                                                                                      
		{                                                                                                 		{                                                                                                 
			                                                                                                 			                                                                                                 
			                                                                                                 			                                                                                                 
			return b;                                                                                        			return b;

public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if ((a>21)&&(b>21))                                                                                 if ((a>21)&&(b>21))                                                                             
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return 0;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        if(a>b && a<21)                                                                                     if(a>b)                                                                                     
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            return a;                                                                                           return a;                                                                               
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        else if(b>a && b<21)                                                                                else if(b>a)                                                                                
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            return b;                                                                                           return b;                                                                               
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
        else                                                                                                else                                                                                        
            return 0;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                               
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
}                                                                                                   }

}                                                                                                   }

    if (a <= 21 && b <= 21)                                                                             if (a <= 21 && b <= 21)                                                                         
   		if (a < b)                                                                                        		if (a < b)                                                                                     
            return b;                                                                                           return b;                                                                               
    	else if (b < a)                                                                                    	else if (b < a)                                                                                
            return a;                                                                                           return a;                                                                               
    return 0;                                                                                           if (a > 21 && b <= 21)                                                                          
}                                                                                                           return b;

                                                                                                        return 0;
