public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int x = 0;                                                                                          int x = 0;                                                                                      
    if (b <= 21)                                                                                        if (b <= 21)                                                                                    
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        if (b > a)                                                                                          if (b > a || a > 21)                                                                        
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
        	x = b;                                                                                             	x = b;                                                                                     
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    if (a <= 21)                                                                                        if (a <= 21)                                                                                    
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        if (a > b)                                                                                          if (a > b || b > 21)                                                                        
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            x = a;                                                                                              x = a;                                                                                  
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    if (a > 21 && b > 21)                                                                               if (a > 21 && b > 21)                                                                           
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        x = 0;                                                                                              x = 0;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return x;					                                                                                      return x;					                                                                                  
}                                                                                                   }

public int sortaSum(int a, int b)                                                                   public int sortaSum(int a, int b)                                                                   
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if ((a+b)>= 10 || (a+b) <= 19)                                                                      if ((a+b)>= 10 && (a+b) <= 19)                                                                  
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return 20;                                                                                          return 20;                                                                                  
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return (a+b);                                                                                       return (a+b);                                                                                   
}                                                                                                   }

	if ((a+b)>= 10 && (a+b) <= 19)                                                                     	if ((a+b)>= 10 && (a+b) <= 19)                                                                     
	{                                                                                                  	{                                                                                                  
		                                                                                                  		                                                                                                  
		                                                                                                  		                                                                                                  
		return 20;                                                                                        		return 20;                                                                                        
		                                                                                                  		                                                                                                  
	}                                                                                                  	}                                                                                                  
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	return (a+b);                                                                                      	return (a+b);                                                                                      
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
}                                                                                                   }

public int sortaSum(int a, int b)                                                                   public int sortaSum(int a, int b)                                                                   
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
 if (a + b >= 10 || a + b <= 19) {                                                                   if (a + b >= 10 && a + b <= 19) {                                                                  
     return 20;                                                                                          return 20;                                                                                     
 }                                                                                                   }                                                                                                  
    else {                                                                                              else {                                                                                          
        return (a+b);                                                                                       return (a+b);                                                                               
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
}                                                                                                   }

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-----------------------------------A1------------------------------------------------------------------------------A2-------------------------------------------------------
public int sortaSum(int a, int b)                                                                   public int sortaSum(int a, int b)                                                                   
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if ( a + b > 9 ||  a + b < 20)                                                                      if ( a + b > 9 &&  a + b < 20)                                                                  
        return 20;                                                                                          return 20;                                                                                  
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
        return a + b;                                                                                       return a + b;                                                                               
}                                                                                                   }                                                                                                   
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
---------------------------------A1+Da----------------------------------------------------------------------------A1+Db-----------------------------------------------------
public int sortaSum(int a, int b)                                                                   public int sortaSum(int a, int b)                                                                   
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	if ( a + b > 9 &&  a + b < 20)                                                                     	if ( a + b > 9 &&  a + b < 20)                                                                     
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	return 20;                                                                                         	return 20;                                                                                         
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	else                                                                                               	else                                                                                               
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	return a + b;                                                                                      	return a + b;                                                                                      
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
}                                                                                                   }

public boolean canBalance(int[] nums)                                                               public boolean canBalance(int[] nums)                                                               
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    return true;                                                                                       int right = 0;                                                                                   
                                                                                                        int left = 0;                                                                                   
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                        for (int i = 0; i < nums.length; i++)                                                           
                                                                                                        {                                                                                               
                                                                                                         right = right + nums[i];                                                                       
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                        for (int i = 0; i < nums.length - 1; i++)                                                       
                                                                                                        {                                                                                               
                                                                                                         left = left + nums[i];                                                                         
                                                                                                            right = right + nums[i];                                                                    
}                                                                                                           if (left == right)                                                                          
                                                                                                            {                                                                                           
                                                                                                             return true;                                                                               
                                                                                                            }                                                                                           
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
                                                                                                        return false;                                                                                   
                                                                                                    }

public boolean in1To10(int n, boolean outsideMode)                                                  public boolean in1To10(int n, boolean outsideMode)                                                  
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	if (n>0 && n<11)                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	return true;                                                                                       	                                                                                                   
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	                                                                                                   	return (n>0 && n<11);                                                                              
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	                                                                                                   }                                                                                                   
	                                                                                                                                                                                                       
	                                                                                                                                                                                                       
	                                                                                                                                                                                                       
	                                                                                                                                                                                                       
	                                                                                                                                                                                                       
	return true;                                                                                                                                                                                           
	                                                                                                                                                                                                       
}

-----------------------------------A1------------------------------------------------------------------------------A2-------------------------------------------------------
public boolean canBalance(int[] nums)                                                               public boolean canBalance(int[] nums)                                                               
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    boolean x = false;                                                                                  boolean x = false;                                                                              
    int sum1 = 0;                                                                                       int sum1 = 0;                                                                                   
    int sum2 = 0;                                                                                       int sum2 = 0;                                                                                   
    int y = 0;                                                                                          int y = 0;                                                                                      
    for (int i = 0; i < nums.length; i++)                                                               for (int i = 0; i < nums.length; i++)                                                           
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
		for (int j = 0; j < nums.length; j++)                                                             		for (int j = 0; j < nums.length; j++)                                                             
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            y = i;                                                                                              y = i + 1;                                                                              
            sum1 += nums[y];                                                                                    sum1 += nums[y];                                                                        
            sum2 += nums[j];                                                                                    sum2 += nums[j];                                                                        
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        sum2 -= sum1;                                                                                       sum2 -= sum1;                                                                               
        if (sum1 == sum2)                                                                                   if (sum1 == sum2)                                                                           
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
			x = true;                                                                                        			x = true;                                                                                        
            break;                                                                                              break;                                                                                  
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return x;                                                                                           return x;                                                                                       
}                                                                                                   }

public boolean canBalance(int[] nums)                                                               public boolean canBalance(int[] nums)                                                               
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	boolean x = false;                                                                                 	boolean x = false;

public boolean canBalance(int[] nums)                                                               public boolean canBalance(int[] nums)                                                               
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    boolean x = false;                                                                                  boolean x = false;                                                                              
    int sum1 = 0;                                                                                       int sum1 = 0;                                                                                   
    int sum2 = 0;                                                                                       int sum2 = 0;                                                                                   
    int y = 0;                                                                                          int y = 0;                                                                                      
    for (int i = 0; i < nums.length; i++)                                                               for (int i = 0; i < nums.length; i++)                                                           
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
		for (int j = 0; j < nums.length; j++)                                                             		for (int j = 0; j < nums.length; j++)                                                             
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            y = i + 1;                                                                                          y = i;                                                                                  
            sum1 += nums[y];                                                                                    sum1 += nums[y];                                                                        
            sum2 += nums[j];                                                                                    sum2 += nums[j];                                                                        
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        sum2 -= sum1;                                                                                       sum2 -= sum1;                                                                               
        if (sum1 == sum2)                                                                                   if (sum1 == sum2)                                                                           
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
			x = true;                                                                                        			x = true;                                                                                        
            break;                                                                                              break;                                                                                  
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return x;                                                                                           return x;                                                                                       
}                                                                                                   }

    	if (str.charAt(i) == 'z' && str.charAt(i+2) == 'p')                                                	if (str.charAt(i) == 'z' && str.charAt(i+2) == 'p')                                            
    	{                                                                                                  	{                                                                                              
        	newStr.deleteCharAt(i+1);                                                                          	newStr.deleteCharAt(i+1);                                                                  
    	}                                                                                                  	}                                                                                              
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return newStr.toString();                                                                           return newStr.toString();                                                                       
}                                                                                                   }

        }                                                                                                   }

public boolean evenlySpaced(int a, int b, int c)                                                    public boolean evenlySpaced(int a, int b, int c)                                                    
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    boolean spacing = false;                                                                            boolean spacing = false;                                                                        
    if (Math.abs(a - b) == Math.abs(b - c))                                                             if ((Math.abs(a - b) == Math.abs(b - c))                                                        
        spacing =  true;                                                                                   || (Math.abs(a-c) == Math.abs(c-b)))                                                         
    return spacing;                                                                                         spacing =  true;                                                                            
}                                                                                                       return spacing;                                                                                 
                                                                                                    }

public boolean evenlySpaced(int a, int b, int c)                                                    public boolean evenlySpaced(int a, int b, int c)

	boolean spacing = false;                                                                           	boolean spacing = false;                                                                           
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	if (Math.abs(a - b) ==  Math.abs(a - c))                                                           	if (Math.abs(a - b) == Math.abs(b - c))                                                            
	spacing =  true;                                                                                   	spacing =  true;                                                                                   
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	                                                                                                   	if (Math.abs(a - c) == Math.abs(b -a))                                                             
	return spacing;                                                                                    	spacing =  true;                                                                                   
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
}                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
                                                                                                    	return spacing;

    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return true;                                                                                        return true;                                                                                
    }                                                                                                   }

    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return true;                                                                                        return true;                                                                                
    }                                                                                                   }

		                                                                                                  		else {                                                                                            
		else {                                                                                            			                                                                                                 
			                                                                                                 			                                                                                                 
			                                                                                                 			return false;                                                                                    
			return false;                                                                                    			                                                                                                 
			                                                                                                 		}                                                                                                 
		}                                                                                                 		                                                                                                  
		                                                                                                  	}                                                                                                  
	}                                                                                                  	                                                                                                   
	                                                                                                   	else {                                                                                             
	else {                                                                                             		                                                                                                  
		                                                                                                  		if (n <= 1) {                                                                                     
		if (n <= 1 && n >= 10) {                                                                          			                                                                                                 
			                                                                                                 			                                                                                                 
			                                                                                                 			return true;                                                                                     
			return true;

public boolean in1To10(int n, boolean outsideMode)                                                  public boolean in1To10(int n, boolean outsideMode)                                                  
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if(!outsideMode && (n <= 10 || n>=1))                                                               if(!outsideMode && (n <= 10 && n>=1))                                                           
        return true;                                                                                        return true;                                                                                
    else if (outsideMode && (n<=1 || n>=10))                                                            else if (outsideMode && (n<=1 || n>=10))                                                        
        return true;                                                                                        return true;                                                                                
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
        return false;                                                                                       return false;                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
}                                                                                                   }

-----------------------------------A1------------------------------------------------------------------------------A2-------------------------------------------------------
public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (a != b && a != c)                                                                               if (a != b && a != c && b != c)                                                                 
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	return a + b + c;                                                                                  	return a + b + c;                                                                             
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a != b && a == c)                                                                          else if (a != b && a == c)                                                                      
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
		return b;                                                                                         		return b;                                                                                         
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a != c && a == b)                                                                          else if (a != c && a == b)                                                                      
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return c;                                                                                           return c;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (b != c && b == a)                                                                          else if (b != c && b == a)                                                                      
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return c;                                                                                           return c;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if  (a != b && b == c)                                                                         else if  (a != b && b == c)                                                                     
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	return a;                                                                                          	return a;                                                                                     
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return 0;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                       
}                                                                                                   }

public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int sum;                                                                                            int sum;                                                                                        
    if (a==b)                                                                                           if (a==b)                                                                                       
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
 		sum = a + c;    	                                                                                 		sum = c;    	                                                                                    
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a==c)                                                                                      else if (a==c)                                                                                  
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	sum = a + b;                                                                                       	sum = b;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (b==c)                                                                                      else if (b==c)                                                                                  
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	sum = a + b;                                                                                       	sum = a;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	sum = a + b + c;                                                                                   	sum = a + b + c;                                                                              
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return sum;                                                                                         return sum;                                                                                     
}                                                                                                   }

{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int sum;                                                                                            int sum;                                                                                        
    if (a==b)                                                                                           if (a==b)                                                                                       
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
 		sum = a + c;    	                                                                                 		sum = c;    	                                                                                    
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a==c)                                                                                      else if (a==c)                                                                                  
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	sum = a + b;                                                                                       	sum = b;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (b==c)                                                                                      else if (b==c)                                                                                  
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	sum = a + b;                                                                                       	sum = a;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	sum = a + b + c;                                                                                   	sum = a + b + c;                                                                              
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return sum;                                                                                         return sum;                                                                                     
}                                                                                                   }

    if (a==b)                                                                                           if (a==b && a==c)                                                                               
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
 		sum = c;    	                                                                                         	sum = 0;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a==c)                                                                                      else if (a==b)                                                                                  
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	sum = b;                                                                                       		sum = c;    	                                                                                    
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (b==c)                                                                                      else if (a==c)                                                                                  
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	sum = a;                                                                                           	sum = b;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a==b && a==c)                                                                              else if (b==c)                                                                                  
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	sum = 0;                                                                                           	sum = a;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	sum = a + b + c;                                                                                   	sum = a + b + c;                                                                              
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return sum;                                                                                         return sum;                                                                                     
}                                                                                                   }

    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a==b && a==c)                                                                              else if (b==c)                                                                                  
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	sum = 0;                                                                                           	sum = a;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	sum = a + b + c;                                                                                   	sum = a + b + c;                                                                              
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return sum;                                                                                         return sum;                                                                                     
}                                                                                                   }

public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
   if (a == b && b!=c) {                                                                               if (a == b && b!=c) {                                                                            
       return a+c;                                                                                         return c;                                                                                    
   }                                                                                                   }                                                                                                
    else if (a==c && b!=c) {                                                                            else if (a==c && b!=c) {                                                                        
        return a+b;                                                                                         return b;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (b == c && a!=b) {                                                                          else if (b == c && a!=b) {                                                                      
        return b+a;                                                                                         return a;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else {                                                                                              else {                                                                                          
        return a+b+c;                                                                                       return a+b+c;                                                                               
	}                                                                                                  	}                                                                                                  
}                                                                                                   }

        a = 0;                                                                                                                                                                                          
    if (b==a || b == c)                                                                                if (a==c)                                                                                        
        b=0;                                                                                           {                                                                                                
    if (c==a || c==b)                                                                                      a=0;                                                                                         
        c=0;                                                                                               c=0;                                                                                         
                                                                                                       }                                                                                                
   if (a==c)                                                                                                                                                                                            
   {                                                                                                     if (a==b)                                                                                      
       a=0;                                                                                            {                                                                                                
       c=0;                                                                                                a=0;                                                                                         
   }                                                                                                       b=0;                                                                                         
                                                                                                       }                                                                                                
     if (a==b)                                                                                                                                                                                          
   {                                                                                                     if (b==c)                                                                                      
       a=0;                                                                                            {                                                                                                
       b=0;                                                                                                b=0;                                                                                         
   }                                                                                                       c=0;                                                                                         
                                                                                                       }                                                                                                
     if (b==c)                                                                                                                                                                                          
   {                                                                                                                                                                                                    
       b=0;                                                                                                                                                                                             
       c=0;                                                                                             if( a == b || a ==c)                                                                            
   }                                                                                                        a = 0;                                                                                      
                                                                                                        if (b==a || b == c)                                                                             
                                                                                                            b=0;                                                                                        
                                                                                                        if (c==a || c==b)                                                                               
    return (a+b+c);                                                                                         c=0;                                                                                        
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
}                                                                                                                                                                                                       
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                        return (a+b+c);

   if (a==c)                                                                                           {                                                                                                
   {                                                                                                       a=0;                                                                                         
       a=0;                                                                                                b=0;                                                                                         
       c=0;                                                                                                c=0;                                                                                         
   }                                                                                                   }                                                                                                
                                                                                                       if (a==c)                                                                                        
     if (a==b)                                                                                         {                                                                                                
   {                                                                                                       a=0;                                                                                         
       a=0;                                                                                                c=0;                                                                                         
       b=0;                                                                                            }                                                                                                
   }                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                         if (a==b)                                                                                      
     if (b==c)                                                                                         {                                                                                                
   {                                                                                                       a=0;                                                                                         
       b=0;                                                                                                b=0;                                                                                         
       c=0;                                                                                            }                                                                                                
   }
