                                                                                                       {                                                                                                
                                                                                                           b=0;                                                                                         
    if( a == b || a ==c)                                                                                   c=0;                                                                                         
        a = 0;                                                                                         }                                                                                                
    if (b==a || b == c)                                                                                                                                                                                 
        b=0;                                                                                                                                                                                            
    if (c==a || c==b)                                                                                                                                                                                   
        c=0;                                                                                            if( a == b || a ==c)                                                                            
                                                                                                            a = 0;

public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                       if (a== b && b == c)                                                                             
   if (a==c)                                                                                           {                                                                                                
   {                                                                                                       a=0;                                                                                         
       a=0;                                                                                                b=0;                                                                                         
       c=0;                                                                                                c=0;                                                                                         
   }                                                                                                   }                                                                                                
                                                                                                       if (a==c)                                                                                        
     if (a==b)                                                                                         {                                                                                                
   {                                                                                                       a=0;                                                                                         
       a=0;                                                                                                c=0;                                                                                         
       b=0;                                                                                            }                                                                                                
   }                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                         if (a==b)                                                                                      
     if (b==c)                                                                                         {                                                                                                
   {                                                                                                       a=0;                                                                                         
       b=0;                                                                                                b=0;                                                                                         
       c=0;                                                                                            }                                                                                                
   }                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                         if (b==c)                                                                                      
                                                                                                       {                                                                                                
                                                                                                           b=0;                                                                                         
    if( a == b || a ==c)                                                                                   c=0;                                                                                         
        a = 0;                                                                                         }                                                                                                
    if (b==a || b == c)                                                                                                                                                                                 
        b=0;                                                                                                                                                                                            
    if (c==a || c==b)                                                                                                                                                                                   
        c=0;                                                                                            if( a == b || a ==c)                                                                            
                                                                                                            a = 0;                                                                                      
                                                                                                        if (b==a || b == c)                                                                             
                                                                                                            b=0;                                                                                        
    return (a+b+c);                                                                                     if (c==a || c==b)                                                                               
                                                                                                            c=0;                                                                                        
}                                                                                                                                                                                                       
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                        return (a+b+c);

public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int x;                                                                                              int x;                                                                                          
    if (a == b && a == c)                                                                               if (a == b && a == c)                                                                           
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        x = 0;                                                                                              x = 0;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (b == a && b == c)                                                                          else if (b == a && b == c)                                                                      
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        x = 0;                                                                                              x = 0;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (c == a && c == a)                                                                          else if (c == b && c == a)                                                                      
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        x = 0;                                                                                              x = 0;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        if (a == b)                                                                                         if (a == b)                                                                                 
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
        	x = c;                                                                                             	x = c;                                                                                     
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        else if (a == c)                                                                                    else if (a == c)                                                                            
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            x = b;                                                                                              x = b;                                                                                  
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        else if (b == c)                                                                                    else if (b == c)                                                                            
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            x = a;                                                                                              x = a;                                                                                  
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        else                                                                                                else                                                                                        
    	{                                                                                                  	{                                                                                              
        	x = a + b + c;                                                                                     	x = a + b + c;                                                                             
    	}                                                                                                  	}                                                                                              
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return x;                                                                                           return x;                                                                                       
}                                                                                                   }

-----------------------------------A1------------------------------------------------------------------------------A2-------------------------------------------------------
public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int sum = a+b+c;                                                                                    int sum = a+b+c;                                                                                
    if (a==b)                                                                                           if (a==b && b==c)                                                                               
        return c;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
    if (c== b)                                                                                          if (a==b)                                                                                       
        return a;                                                                                           return c;                                                                                   
    if (a==c)                                                                                           if (c== b)                                                                                      
        return b;                                                                                           return a;                                                                                   
                                                                                                        if (a==c)                                                                                       
    else                                                                                                    return b;                                                                                   
        return sum;                                                                                                                                                                                     
}                                                                                                       else                                                                                            
                                                                                                            return sum;                                                                                 
                                                                                                    }

---------------------------------A1+Da----------------------------------------------------------------------------A1+Db-----------------------------------------------------
public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	int sum = a+b+c;                                                                                   	int sum = a+b+c;                                                                                   
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	if (a==b)                                                                                          	if (a==b && b==c)                                                                                  
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	return c;                                                                                          	return 0;                                                                                          
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	if (c== b)                                                                                         	if (a==b)                                                                                          
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	return a;                                                                                          	return c;                                                                                          
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	if (a==c)                                                                                          	if (c== b)                                                                                         
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	return b;                                                                                          	return a;                                                                                          
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	                                                                                                   	if (a==c)                                                                                          
	else                                                                                               	                                                                                                   
	                                                                                                   	return b;                                                                                          
	return sum;                                                                                        	                                                                                                   
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
}                                                                                                   	else                                                                                               
                                                                                                    	                                                                                                   
                                                                                                    	return sum;                                                                                        
                                                                                                    	                                                                                                   
                                                                                                    }

-----------------------------------A1------------------------------------------------------------------------------A2-------------------------------------------------------
public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int sum = a+b+c;                                                                                    int sum = a+b+c;                                                                                
    if (a==b)                                                                                           if (a==b && b==c)                                                                               
        return c;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
    if (c== b)                                                                                          if (a==b)                                                                                       
        return a;                                                                                           return c;                                                                                   
    if (a==c)                                                                                           if (c== b)                                                                                      
        return b;                                                                                           return a;                                                                                   
                                                                                                        if (a==c)                                                                                       
    else                                                                                                    return b;                                                                                   
        return sum;                                                                                                                                                                                     
}                                                                                                       else                                                                                            
                                                                                                            return sum;                                                                                 
                                                                                                    }

{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	int sum = a+b+c;                                                                                   	int sum = a+b+c;                                                                                   
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	if (a==b)                                                                                          	if (a==b && b==c)                                                                                  
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	return c;                                                                                          	return 0;                                                                                          
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	if (c== b)                                                                                         	if (a==b)                                                                                          
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	return a;                                                                                          	return c;                                                                                          
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	if (a==c)                                                                                          	if (c== b)                                                                                         
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	return b;                                                                                          	return a;                                                                                          
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	                                                                                                   	if (a==c)                                                                                          
	else                                                                                               	                                                                                                   
	                                                                                                   	return b;                                                                                          
	return sum;

        return c;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
    if (c== b)                                                                                          if (a==b)

        return b;                                                                                           return a;

    else                                                                                                    return b;                                                                                   
        return sum;                                                                                                                                                                                     
}                                                                                                       else                                                                                            
                                                                                                            return sum;

    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
    	return a+c;                                                                                        	return c;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a == c)                                                                                    else if (a == c)                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
    	return a + b;                                                                                      	return b;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (b == c)                                                                                    else if (b == c)                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
    	return a+b;                                                                                        	return a;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }

public String getSandwich(String str)                                                               public String getSandwich(String str)                                                               
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (str.startsWith("bread") && str.endsWith("bread"))                                               int first = str.indexOf("bread");                                                               
    {                                                                                                   int last = str.lastIndexOf("bread");                                                            
        return str.substring(5, str.length()-5);                                                        if (first != last)                                                                              
    }                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                    return str.substring(first+5, last);                                                        
    {                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
        return "";                                                                                      else                                                                                            
    }                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
}                                                                                                           return "";                                                                                  
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
                                                                                                    }

public String getSandwich(String str)                                                               public String getSandwich(String str)                                                               
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int first = -1;                                                                                     int first = -1;                                                                                 
    int last = -1;                                                                                      int last = -1;                                                                                  
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                        for(int i = 0; i < str.length() - 5; i++) {                                                     
                                                                                                            if(str.substring(i, i + 5).equals("bread"))                                                 
                                                                                                            {                                                                                           
    if(first != -1 && last != -1 && first != last)                                                              first = i;                                                                              
    {                                                                                                           break;                                                                                  
		return str.substring(first + 5, last);                                                                    }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                                                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   for(int i = str.length() - 5; i >= 0; i--)                                                      
        return"";                                                                                       {                                                                                               
    }                                                                                                       if(str.substring(i, i + 5).equals("bread"))                                                 
}                                                                                                           {                                                                                           
                                                                                                                last = i;                                                                               
                                                                                                                break;                                                                                  
                                                                                                            }                                                                                           
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
                                                                                                        if (first != last && first != -1 && last != -1)                                                 
                                                                                                        {                                                                                               
                                                                                                            return str.substring(first + 5, last);                                                      
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
                                                                                                        else                                                                                            
                                                                                                        {                                                                                               
                                                                                                            return"";

{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (isBirthday)                                                                                     if (isBirthday)                                                                                 
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        if (speed <= 60)                                                                                     if (speed <= 65)                                                                           
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            return 0;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                               
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        else if (speed > 60 && speed <= 80)                                                                 else if (speed >= 66 && speed <= 85)                                                        
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            return 1;                                                                                           return 1;                                                                               
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        else                                                                                                else                                                                                        
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            return 2;                                                                                           return 2;                                                                               
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
                                                                                                    	}                                                                                                  
	}                                                                                                      else                                                                                            
    else                                                                                                {                                                                                               
    {                                                                                                      if (speed <= 60)                                                                             
         if (speed <= 65)                                                                                   {                                                                                           
        {                                                                                                       return 0;                                                                               
            return 0;                                                                                       }

public boolean isEverywhere(int[] nums, int val)                                                    public boolean isEverywhere(int[] nums, int val)                                                    
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    boolean x = false;                                                                                  boolean x = false;                                                                              
    for (int i = 0; i < nums.length; i++)                                                               for (int i = 0; i < nums.length; i++)                                                           
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	if (i == 0 && (i + 2) != nums.length)                                                              	if (i == 0 && (i + 1) != nums.length)                                                         
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            if (nums[i+1] == val || nums[i+2] == val)                                                           if (nums[i] == val || nums[i+1] == val)                                                 
            {                                                                                                   {                                                                                       
                x = true;                                                                                           x = true;                                                                           
            }                                                                                                   }                                                                                       
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return x;                                                                                           return x;                                                                                       
}                                                                                                   }

public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int diffA = 21 - a;                                                                                 int diffA = 21 - a;                                                                             
    int diffB = 21 - a;                                                                                 int diffB = 21 - a;                                                                             
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    if ((diffA < 0) && (diffB <0))                                                                      if ((diffA < 0) && (diffB <0))                                                                  
    	return 0;                                                                                          	return 0;                                                                                      
    else if (diffA < 0)                                                                                 else if (diffA < 0)                                                                             
        return b;                                                                                           return b;                                                                                   
    else if (diffB < 0)                                                                                 else if (diffB < 0)                                                                             
        return a;                                                                                           return a;                                                                                   
    else if (diffB > diffA)                                                                             else if (diffB > diffA)                                                                         
        return a;                                                                                           return b;                                                                                   
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
        return b;                                                                                           return a;                                                                                   
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
}                                                                                                   }

    {                                                                                                   	for (int i = str.lastIndexOf("x"); i < str.length(); i++)

         		return true;                                                                                     	}

    	}

    return false;                                                                                   }                                                                                                   
}

public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    a = a - 21;                                                                                         int a1 = a - 21;                                                                                
    b = b - 21;                                                                                         int b1 = b - 21;                                                                                
    if (a < 0 && b < 0)                                                                                 if (a1 < 0 && b1 < 0)                                                                           
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return 0;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        if (a > b)                                                                                          if (a1 > b1)                                                                                
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            return b;                                                                                           return b;                                                                               
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        else                                                                                                else                                                                                        
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            return a;                                                                                           return a;                                                                               
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
}                                                                                                   }

		return 0;                                                                                         		return 0;

	else                                                                                               	else

			return a;                                                                                        			return a;

public boolean evenlySpaced(int a, int b, int c)                                                    public boolean evenlySpaced(int a, int b, int c)                                                    
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int temp;                                                                                           int temp;                                                                                       
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    if (a>b)                                                                                            if (a>b)                                                                                        
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        temp = a;                                                                                           temp = a;                                                                                   
        a = b;                                                                                              a = b;                                                                                      
        b = temp;                                                                                           b = temp;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    if (b>c)                                                                                            if (b>c)                                                                                        
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        temp = b;                                                                                           temp = b;                                                                                   
        b = c;                                                                                              b = c;                                                                                      
        c = temp;                                                                                           c = temp;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    if (a>b)                                                                                            if (a>b)                                                                                        
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        temp = a;                                                                                           temp = a;                                                                                   
        a = b;                                                                                              a = b;                                                                                      
        b = temp;                                                                                           b = temp;                                                                                   
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    return (b - a == c - b);                                                                            return (b - a == c - b);                                                                        
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    return true;                                                                                        return false;                                                                                   
}                                                                                                   }

public boolean evenlySpaced(int a, int b, int c)                                                    public boolean evenlySpaced(int a, int b, int c)                                                    
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	int temp;                                                                                          	int temp;                                                                                          
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	if (a>b)                                                                                           	if (a>b)

public boolean isEverywhere(int[] nums, int val)                                                    public boolean isEverywhere(int[] nums, int val)                                                    
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    boolean everywhere = false;                                                                         boolean everywhere = false;                                                                     
    int numTimes = 0;                                                                                   int numTimes = 0;                                                                               
    for (int i = 0; i < nums.length; i++)                                                               for (int i = 0; i < nums.length; i++)                                                           
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        int maxValue = i;                                                                                   int maxValue = i;                                                                           
        if (i + 1 < nums.length)                                                                            if (i + 1 < nums.length)                                                                    
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            maxValue++;                                                                                         maxValue++;                                                                             
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        if (nums[i] == val || nums[maxValue] == val)                                                        if (nums[i] == val || nums[maxValue] == val)                                                
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            numTimes++;                                                                                         numTimes++;                                                                             
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    if (numTimes >= nums.length * 2)                                                                    if (numTimes >= nums.length / 2)                                                                
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        everywhere = true;                                                                                  everywhere = true;                                                                          
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return everywhere;                                                                                  return everywhere;                                                                              
}                                                                                                   }

public boolean canBalance(int[] nums)                                                               public boolean canBalance(int[] nums)                                                               
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    Boolean in = false;                                                                                 Boolean in = false;                                                                             
    int t1= 0;                                                                                          int t1= 0;                                                                                      
    int t2 = 0;                                                                                         int t2 = 0;                                                                                     
    for( int i = 1; i < nums.length; i++)                                                               for( int i = 1; i < nums.length; i++)                                                           
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        for ( int y = i ; y < nums.length; y++)                                                             for ( int y = i ; y < nums.length; y++)                                                     
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            t2 = t2 + nums[y];                                                                                  t2 = t2 + nums[y];                                                                      
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        for ( int f = 0 ; f < i; i++)                                                                       for ( int f = 0 ; f< i; f++)                                                                
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            t1 = t1 + nums[f];                                                                                  t1 = t1 + nums[f];                                                                      
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        if (t1== t2)                                                                                        if ( t1==t2)                                                                                
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            return true;                                                                                        return true;                                                                            
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return in;                                                                                          return in;                                                                                      
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
}                                                                                                   }

        return c;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a == c)                                                                                    else if (a == b)

    }                                                                                                   }
