public boolean canBalance(int[] nums)                                                               public boolean canBalance(int[] nums)                                                               
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    boolean x = false;                                                                                  boolean x = false;                                                                              
    int sum1 = 0;                                                                                       int sum1 = 0;                                                                                   
    int sum2 = 0;                                                                                       int sum2 = 0;                                                                                   
    int y = 0;                                                                                          int y = 0;                                                                                      
    for (int i = 0; i < nums.length; i++)                                                               for (int i = 0; i < nums.length; i++)                                                           
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
		for (int j = 0; j < nums.length; j++)                                                             		for (int j = 0; j < nums.length; j++)                                                             
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            y = i;                                                                                              y = i + 1;                                                                              
            sum1 += nums[y];                                                                                    sum1 += nums[y];                                                                        
            sum2 += nums[j];                                                                                    sum2 += nums[j];                                                                        
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        sum2 -= sum1;                                                                                       sum2 -= sum1;                                                                               
        if (sum1 == sum2)                                                                                   if (sum1 == sum2)                                                                           
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
			x = true;                                                                                        			x = true;                                                                                        
            break;                                                                                              break;                                                                                  
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return x;                                                                                           return x;                                                                                       
}                                                                                                   }

            }                                                                                                   }

}                                                                                                   }

        	x = b;                                                                                             	x = b;

    }                                                                                                   }

     	x = true;                                                                                          	x = true;                                                                                     
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else

        x = false;                                                                                          x = false;                                                                                  
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return x;                                                                                           return x;                                                                                       
}                                                                                                   }

public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int sum = 0;                                                                                        int sum = 0;                                                                                    
    if (a == b)                                                                                         if (a == b && b == c)                                                                           
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        sum = a + c;                                                                                        // do nothing                                                                               
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a == c)                                                                                    else if (a == b)                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        sum = a + b;                                                                                        sum = c;                                                                                    
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (b == c)                                                                                    else if (a == c)                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        sum = a + b;                                                                                        sum = a;                                                                                    
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else if (b == c)                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        sum = a + b + c;                                                                                    sum = a;                                                                                    
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return sum;                                                                                         else                                                                                            
}                                                                                                       {                                                                                               
                                                                                                            sum = a + b + c;                                                                            
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
                                                                                                        return sum;                                                                                     
                                                                                                    }

	}                                                                                                  	}                                                                                                  
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	else if (a == c)                                                                                   	else if (a == c)

		sum = b;                                                                                          		sum = b;

{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    return true;                                                                                        int front = nums[0];                                                                            
}                                                                                                       int tail = 0;                                                                                   
                                                                                                        int j =0;                                                                                       
                                                                                                        int i =0;                                                                                       
                                                                                                        if( front < tail)                                                                               
                                                                                                        {                                                                                               
                                                                                                             for(;i<nums.length;i++)                                                                    
                                                                                                       		 {                                                                                             
                                                                                                            front += nums[i];                                                                           
                                                                                                             }                                                                                          
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
                                                                                                        else if(front>tail)                                                                             
                                                                                                        {                                                                                               
                                                                                                            for(;j>i;j--)                                                                               
                                                                                                            {                                                                                           
                                                                                                                tail+=nums[j];                                                                          
                                                                                                            }                                                                                           
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                        return front==tail;                                                                             
                                                                                                    }

-----------------------------------A1------------------------------------------------------------------------------A2-------------------------------------------------------
public boolean canBalance(int[] nums)                                                               public boolean canBalance(int[] nums)                                                               
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int left;                                                                                           int left = 0;                                                                                   
    int right = 0;                                                                                  	int right;                                                                                         
                                                                                                    	for (int i = 0; i < nums.length - 1; i++)                                                          
	for (int i = 0; i < nums.length - 1; i++)                                                              {                                                                                               
    {                                                                                               		left += nums[i];                                                                                  
		right += nums[i];                                                                                     }                                                                                               
    }                                                                                               	right = nums[nums.length-1];                                                                       
	left = nums[nums.length - 1];                                                                      	for (int i = nums.length - 2; i > 0; i--)                                                          
                                                                                                    	{                                                                                                  
	for (int i = nums.length - 2; i > 0; i--)                                                          		if (left == right)                                                                                
	{                                                                                                          {                                                                                           
		if(left == right)                                                                                 			return true;                                                                                     
        {                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
			return true;                                                                                     		left = left - nums[i];                                                                            
        }                                                                                           		right = right + nums[i];                                                                          
		left = left - nums[i];                                                                            	}                                                                                                  
		right = right + nums[i];                                                                          	return (left == right);                                                                            
	}                                                                                                  }                                                                                                   
	return (left == right);                                                                                                                                                                                
}

---------------------------------A1+Da----------------------------------------------------------------------------A1+Db-----------------------------------------------------
public boolean canBalance(int[] nums)                                                               public boolean canBalance(int[] nums)                                                               
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	int left = 0;                                                                                      	int left = 0;                                                                                      
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	int right;                                                                                         	int right;                                                                                         
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	for(int i = 0;                                                                                     	for(int i = 0;                                                                                     
	i < nums.length - 1;                                                                               	i < nums.length - 1;                                                                               
	i++)                                                                                               	i++)                                                                                               
	{                                                                                                  	{

public boolean evenlySpaced(int a, int b, int c)                                                    public boolean evenlySpaced(int a, int b, int c)                                                    
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
	int x = Math.abs(a-b);                                                                             	//t x = Math.abs(a-b);                                                                             
    int y = Math.abs(b-c);                                                                              //t y = Math.abs(b-c);                                                                          
    int z = Math.abs(a-c);                                                                              //t z = Math.abs(a-c);                                                                          
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    int sum = x+y+z;                                                                                    int sum = a+b+c;                                                                                
    int avg = sum/3;                                                                                    int avg = sum/3;                                                                                
    int j = Math.abs(avg - a);                                                                          int j = Math.abs(avg - a);                                                                      
    int k = Math.abs(avg - b);                                                                          int k = Math.abs(avg - b);                                                                      
    int g = Math.abs(avg - c);                                                                          int g = Math.abs(avg - c);                                                                      
    if (a == avg || b == avg || c == avg)                                                               if (a == avg || b == avg || c == avg)                                                           
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    	if ( j == k || k==g || j==g)                                                                       	if ( j == k || k==g || j==g)                                                                   
            return true;                                                                                        return true;                                                                            
        else return false;                                                                                  else return false;                                                                          
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
        return false;                                                                                       return false;                                                                               
}                                                                                                   }

    {                                                                                               			return false;                                                                                    
        int maxValue = i;                                                                           	}                                                                                                  
        if (i + 1 < nums.length)                                                                    	return true;                                                                                       
        {                                                                                           }                                                                                                   
            maxValue++;

        if (nums[i] == val || nums[maxValue] == val)                                                                                                                                                    
        {                                                                                                                                                                                               
            numTimes++;                                                                                                                                                                                 
        }                                                                                                                                                                                               
    }                                                                                                                                                                                                   
    if (numTimes * 2 >= nums.length)                                                                                                                                                                    
    {                                                                                                                                                                                                   
        everywhere = true;                                                                                                                                                                              
    }                                                                                                                                                                                                   
    return everywhere;                                                                                                                                                                                  
}

public boolean evenlySpaced(int a, int b, int c)                                                    public boolean evenlySpaced(int a, int b, int c)                                                    
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int evenlySpaced;                                                                                   int evenlySpaced;                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    if (a > b)                                                                                          if (a > b)                                                                                      
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	evenlySpaced = b;                                                                                  	evenlySpaced = b;                                                                             
        b = a;                                                                                              b = a;                                                                                      
        a = evenlySpaced;                                                                                   a = evenlySpaced;                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    else if (b > c)                                                                                     else if (b > c)                                                                                 
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	evenlySpaced = c;                                                                                  	evenlySpaced = c;                                                                             
        c = b;                                                                                              c = b;                                                                                      
        b = evenlySpaced;                                                                                   b = evenlySpaced;                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    else if (c > a)                                                                                     else if (c > a)                                                                                 
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	evenlySpaced = a;                                                                                  	evenlySpaced = a;                                                                             
        a = c;                                                                                              a = c;                                                                                      
        c = evenlySpaced;                                                                                   c = evenlySpaced;                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    return (a - b == c - b);                                                                            return (a - b == b - c);                                                                        
}                                                                                                   }

{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
	if(a > 12 && a < 20)                                                                               	return (fixTeen(a) + fixTeen(b) + fixTeen(c));                                                     
    {                                                                                               }

    }                                                                                               {

public boolean canBalance(int[] nums)                                                               public boolean canBalance(int[] nums)                                                               
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    boolean x = false;                                                                                  boolean x = false;                                                                              
    int sum1 = 0;                                                                                       int sum1 = 0;                                                                                   
    int sum2 = 0;                                                                                       int sum2 = 0;                                                                                   
    for (int i = 0; i < nums.length; i++)                                                               for (int i = 0; i < nums.length; i++)                                                           
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
		for (int j = 0; j < nums.length; j++)                                                             		for (int j = 0; j < nums.length; j++)                                                             
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            j = i + 1;                                                                                          j = i;                                                                                  
            sum1 += nums[j];                                                                                    sum1 += nums[j];                                                                        
            sum2 += nums[j];                                                                                    sum2 += nums[j];                                                                        
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        sum2 -= sum1;                                                                                       sum2 -= sum1;                                                                               
        if (sum1 == sum2)                                                                                   if (sum1 == sum2)                                                                           
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
			x = true;                                                                                        			x = true;                                                                                        
            break;                                                                                              break;                                                                                  
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return x;                                                                                           return x;                                                                                       
}                                                                                                   }

public boolean evenlySpaced(int a, int b, int c)                                                    public boolean evenlySpaced(int a, int b, int c)                                                    
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int small = 0;                                                                                      int small = 0;                                                                                  
    int medium = 0;                                                                                     int medium = 0;                                                                                 
    int large = 0;                                                                                      int large = 0;                                                                                  
    if (a > b && a > c)                                                                                 if (a > b && a > c)                                                                             
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        large = a;                                                                                          large = a;                                                                                  
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a < b && a > c)                                                                            else if (a <= b && a >= c)                                                                      
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        medium = a;                                                                                         medium = a;                                                                                 
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a > b && a < c)                                                                            else if (a >= b && a <= c)                                                                      
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        medium = a;                                                                                         medium = a;                                                                                 
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        small = a;                                                                                          small = a;                                                                                  
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    if (b > a && b > c)                                                                                 if (b > a && b > c)                                                                             
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        large = b;                                                                                          large = b;                                                                                  
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (b < a && b > c)                                                                            else if (b < a && b > c)                                                                        
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        medium = b;                                                                                         medium = b;                                                                                 
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (b > a && b < c)                                                                            else if (b > a && b < c)                                                                        
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        medium = b;                                                                                         medium = b;                                                                                 
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        small = b;                                                                                          small = b;                                                                                  
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    if (large == 0)                                                                                     if (large == 0)                                                                                 
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        large = c;                                                                                          large = c;                                                                                  
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (medium == 0)                                                                               else if (medium == 0)                                                                           
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        medium = c;                                                                                         medium = c;                                                                                 
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        small = c;                                                                                          small = c;                                                                                  
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    if ((large - medium) == (medium - small))                                                           if ((large - medium) == (medium - small))                                                       
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return true;                                                                                        return true;                                                                                
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return false;                                                                                       return false;                                                                               
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
}                                                                                                   }

    if (a == b && a == c)                                                                               return (a + b + c);                                                                             
        return 0;                                                                                   }                                                                                                   
    return (a + b + c);                                                                                                                                                                                 
}

public boolean evenlySpaced(int a, int b, int c)                                                    public boolean evenlySpaced(int a, int b, int c)                                                    
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int evenlySpaced;                                                                                   int evenlySpaced;                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    if (a > b)                                                                                          if (a > b)                                                                                      
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	evenlySpaced = b;                                                                                  	evenlySpaced = b;                                                                             
        b = a;                                                                                              b = a;                                                                                      
        a = evenlySpaced;                                                                                   a = evenlySpaced;                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    else if (b > c)                                                                                     else if (b > c)                                                                                 
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	evenlySpaced = c;                                                                                  	evenlySpaced = c;                                                                             
        c = b;                                                                                              c = b;                                                                                      
        b = evenlySpaced;                                                                                   b = evenlySpaced;                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    else if (c > a)                                                                                     else if (c > a)                                                                                 
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	evenlySpaced = a;                                                                                  	evenlySpaced = a;                                                                             
        a = c;                                                                                              a = c;                                                                                      
        c = evenlySpaced;                                                                                   c = evenlySpaced;                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    return (a - b == b - c);                                                                            return (a - b == c - b);                                                                        
}                                                                                                   }

public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  public int blackjack(int a, int b)

    }                                                                                                       bj=b;                                                                                       
    else if(diffa<diffb)                                                                                }                                                                                               
    {                                                                                                   if(db>da)                                                                                       
        blackjack=a;                                                                                    {

public boolean answerCell(boolean isMorning, boolean isMom, boolean isAsleep)                       public boolean answerCell(boolean isMorning, boolean isMom, boolean isAsleep)                       
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (isMorning && isMom && !isAsleep)                                                                if (isMorning && isMom && !isAsleep)                                                            
        return true;                                                                                        return true;                                                                                
    if (!isMorning && !isMom && !isAsleep)                                                              if (!(isMorning && isMom && isAsleep))                                                          
        return true;                                                                                        return true;                                                                                
    return false;                                                                                       return false;                                                                                   
}                                                                                                   }

public boolean answerCell(boolean isMorning, boolean isMom, boolean isAsleep)                       public boolean answerCell(boolean isMorning, boolean isMom, boolean isAsleep)                       
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	if (isMorning && isMom &&!isAsleep)                                                                	if (isMorning && isMom &&!isAsleep)                                                                
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	return true;                                                                                       	return true;                                                                                       
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	if (!isMorning &&!isMom &&!isAsleep)                                                               	if (!(isMorning && isMom && isAsleep))                                                             
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	return true;                                                                                       	return true;                                                                                       
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	return false;                                                                                      	return false;                                                                                      
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
}                                                                                                   }

		}                                                                                                 		}

	                                                                                                   		return true;

    	{                                                                                                   	return true;                                                                                  
     		if (str.charAt(i) == 'y')                                                                        }                                                                                               
        	{                                                                                              	for (int i = str.lastIndexOf("x"); i < str.length(); i++)                                      
         		return true;                                                                                 	{                                                                                              
        	}                                                                                               		if (str.charAt(i) == 'y')                                                                    
    	}                                                                                                      	{

    return false;                                                                                           	}                                                                                          
}                                                                                                       	}

public boolean canBalance(int[] nums)                                                               public boolean canBalance(int[] nums)                                                               
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    boolean x = false;                                                                                  boolean x = false;                                                                              
    int sum1 = 0;                                                                                       int sum1 = 0;                                                                                   
    int sum2 = 0;                                                                                       int sum2 = 0;                                                                                   
    for (int i = 0; i < nums.length; i++)                                                               for (int i = 0; i < nums.length; i++)                                                           
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
		for (int j = 0; j < nums.length; j++)                                                             		for (int j = 0; j < nums.length; j++)                                                             
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            sum1 += nums[j - i];                                                                                j = i + 1;                                                                              
            sum2 += nums[j];                                                                                    sum1 += nums[j];                                                                        
        }                                                                                                       sum2 += nums[j];                                                                        
        sum2 -= sum1;                                                                                       }                                                                                           
        if (sum1 == sum2)                                                                                   sum2 -= sum1;                                                                               
        {                                                                                                   if (sum1 == sum2)                                                                           
			x = true;                                                                                                {                                                                                           
            break;                                                                                  			x = true;                                                                                        
        }                                                                                                       break;                                                                                  
    }                                                                                                       }                                                                                           
    return x;                                                                                           }                                                                                               
}                                                                                                       return x;                                                                                       
                                                                                                    }

	for (int i = 0;                                                                                    	for (int i = 0;                                                                                    
	i < nums.length;                                                                                   	i < nums.length;                                                                                   
	i++)                                                                                               	i++)                                                                                               
	{                                                                                                  	{                                                                                                  
		                                                                                                  		                                                                                                  
		for (int j = 0;                                                                                   		for (int j = 0;

		sum2 -= sum1;                                                                                     		sum2 -= sum1;

public int caughtSpeeding(int speed, boolean isBirthday)                                            public int caughtSpeeding(int speed, boolean isBirthday)                                            
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (isBirthday == true)                                                                             if (isBirthday == true)                                                                         
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        speed = speed + 5;                                                                                  speed = speed - 5;                                                                          
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    if (speed >= 81)                                                                                    if (speed >= 81)                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return 2;                                                                                           return 2;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (speed < 81 && speed >= 61)                                                                 else if (speed < 81 && speed >= 61)                                                             
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return 1;                                                                                           return 1;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return 0;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
}                                                                                                   }
