public int fixTeen(int n)                                                                           public int fixTeen(int n)                                                                           
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
 if (n < 13 || n < 19 || n == 15 || n == 16) {                                                       if (n <= 13 || n >= 19 || n == 15 || n == 16) {                                                    
     return n;                                                                                           return n;                                                                                      
 }                                                                                                   }                                                                                                  
    else {                                                                                              else {                                                                                          
        return 0;                                                                                           return 0;

public String zipZap(String str)                                                                    public String zipZap(String str)                                                                    
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    String newStr = "";                                                                                 String newStr = "";                                                                             
    int i = 0;                                                                                          int i = 0;                                                                                      
    while(i < str.length()-2)                                                                           while(i < str.length())                                                                         
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        String strA = Character.toString(str.charAt(i));                                                    String strA = Character.toString(str.charAt(i));                                            
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
        if ((str.charAt(i) == 'z') && (str.charAt(i+2) == 'p'))                                             if ((str.charAt(i) == 'z') && (str.charAt(i+2) == 'p') && (i < str.length()-2))             
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            newStr = newStr.concat(strA);                                                                       newStr = newStr.concat("zp");                                                           
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
            i = i+2;                                                                                            i = i+3;                                                                                
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        else                                                                                                else                                                                                        
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            newStr = newStr.concat(strA);                                                                       newStr = newStr.concat(strA);                                                           
            i++;                                                                                                i++;                                                                                    
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    newStr = newStr.concat("p");                                                                        newStr = newStr.concat("p");                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    return newStr;                                                                                      return newStr;                                                                                  
}                                                                                                   }

public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  
{                                                                                                   {

    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	return a;                                                                                          	return 0;                                                                                     
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (b > a && b <= 21)                                                                                                                                                                          
    {                                                                                                   if (a > 21)                                                                                     
     	return b;                                                                                         {                                                                                               
    }                                                                                                    	return b;                                                                                     
    else if (a == b && a <= 21)                                                                         }                                                                                               
    {                                                                                                   else if (b > 21)                                                                                
     	return a;                                                                                         {                                                                                               
    }                                                                                                    	return a;                                                                                     
    else                                                                                                }                                                                                               
    {                                                                                                   else if (a > b)                                                                                 
     	return 0;                                                                                         {                                                                                               
    }                                                                                                    	return a;                                                                                     
}                                                                                                       }                                                                                               
                                                                                                        else                                                                                            
                                                                                                        {                                                                                               
                                                                                                         	return b;                                                                                     
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
                                                                                                    }

public int noTeenSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                           public int noTeenSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                           
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    a = fixTeen(a);                                                                                     a = fixTeen(a);                                                                                 
    b = fixTeen(b);                                                                                     b = fixTeen(b);                                                                                 
    c = fixTeen(c);                                                                                     c = fixTeen(c);                                                                                 
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    return a + b + c;                                                                                   return a + b + c;                                                                               
}                                                                                                   }                                                                                                   
public int fixTeen(int n)                                                                           public int fixTeen(int n)                                                                           
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
if (n >= 13 && n<= 19)                                                                              if (n >= 13 && n<= 19)                                                                              
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (n != 15 || n != 16)                                                                             if (n == 15 || n == 16)                                                                         
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return n;                                                                                           return n;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
}                                                                                                   }                                                                                                   
        return 0;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
}                                                                                                   }

	return a + b + c;                                                                                  	return a + b + c;

public String zipZap(String str)                                                                    public String zipZap(String str)                                                                    
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    String newStr = "";                                                                                 String newStr = "";                                                                             
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    for (int i = 1; i <= str.length()-2; i++)                                                           for (int i = 0; i < str.length()-2; i++)                                                        
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        if ((str.charAt(i) == 'z') && (str.charAt(i+2) == 'p'))                                             if ((str.charAt(i) == 'z') && (str.charAt(i+2) == 'p'))                                     
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            String strA= Character.toString(str.charAt(i+1));                                                   String strA= Character.toString(str.charAt(i+1));                                       
            newStr = str.replaceFirst(strA, "");                                                                newStr = str.replaceFirst(strA, "");                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    return newStr;                                                                                      return newStr;                                                                                  
}                                                                                                   }

public String zipZap(String str)                                                                    public String zipZap(String str)                                                                    
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	String newStr = "";                                                                                	String newStr = "";                                                                                
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	for (int i = 0;                                                                                    	for (int i = 0;                                                                                    
	i < str.length();                                                                                  	i < str.length();

public boolean canBalance(int[] nums)                                                               public boolean canBalance(int[] nums)                                                               
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int sum = 0;                                                                                        int sum = 0;                                                                                    
    for (int num: nums)                                                                                 for (int num: nums)                                                                             
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        sum = sum + num;                                                                                    sum = sum + num;                                                                            
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    int half = sum/2;                                                                                   int half = sum/2;                                                                               
    sum = 0;                                                                                            sum = 0;                                                                                        
    for (int num: nums)                                                                                 int secondSum = 0;                                                                              
    {                                                                                                   for (int num: nums)                                                                             
        sum = sum + num;                                                                                {                                                                                               
        if (sum == half)                                                                                                                                                                                
        {                                                                                                   if (sum != half)                                                                            
            return true;                                                                                    {                                                                                           
        }                                                                                                       sum = sum + num;                                                                        
    }                                                                                                       }                                                                                           
                                                                                                            else                                                                                        
    return false;                                                                                           {                                                                                           
                                                                                                                secondSum = secondSum + num;                                                            
}                                                                                                           }                                                                                           
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                        return secondSum == half;                                                                       
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                    }

public boolean evenlySpaced(int a, int b, int c)                                                    public boolean evenlySpaced(int a, int b, int c)                                                    
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
	int x = Math.abs(a-b);                                                                             	int x = Math.abs(a-b);                                                                             
    int y = Math.abs(b-c);                                                                              int y = Math.abs(b-c);                                                                          
    int z = Math.abs(a-c);                                                                              int z = Math.abs(a-c);                                                                          
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    int sum = x+y+z;                                                                                    int sum = x+y+z;                                                                                
    int avg = sum/3;                                                                                    int avg = sum/3;                                                                                
    int j = Math.abs(avg - a);                                                                          int j = Math.abs(avg - a);                                                                      
    int k = Math.abs(avg - b);                                                                          int k = Math.abs(avg - b);                                                                      
    int g = Math.abs(avg - c);                                                                          int g = Math.abs(avg - c);                                                                      
    if (a == avg || b == avg || c == avg)                                                               if (a == avg || b == avg || c == avg)                                                           
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    	if ( j == k || k==g || j==g)                                                                       	if ( j == k || k==g || j==g)                                                                   
            return true;                                                                                        return true;                                                                            
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
        return false;                                                                                       return false;                                                                               
  return false;                                                                                       return true;                                                                                      
}                                                                                                   }

public boolean xyBalance(String str)                                                                public boolean xyBalance(String str)                                                                
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int good = 0;                                                                                       int good = 0;

    for (int lookX = 0; lookX < str.length(); lookX++)                                                  for (int lookX = 0; lookX < str.length(); lookX++)                                              
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        char x = str.charAt(lookX);                                                                         char x = str.charAt(lookX);                                                                 
    	for (int lookY = str.indexOf(x); lookY < str.length(); 			lookY++)                                 	for (int lookY = str.indexOf(x); lookY < str.length(); 			lookY++)                             
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            char y = str.charAt(lookY);                                                                         char y = str.charAt(lookY);                                                             
    		if (str.indexOf(y) > x)                                                                           		if (str.indexOf(y) > str.indexOf(x))                                                          
            {                                                                                                   {                                                                                       
                good++;                                                                                             good++;                                                                             
            }                                                                                                   }

                bad++;                                                                                              bad++;                                                                              
            }                                                                                                   }                                                                                       
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    if (bad > 0)                                                                                        if (bad > 0)                                                                                    
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
    	return false;                                                                                      	return false;                                                                                  
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return true;                                                                                        return true;                                                                                    
}                                                                                                   }

public boolean xyBalance(String str)                                                                public boolean xyBalance(String str)                                                                
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int index1=0;                                                                                       int index1=0;                                                                                   
    int index2=0;                                                                                       int index2=0;                                                                                   
    for(int i=str.length();i>0;i--)                                                                     for(int i=str.length();i>0;i--)                                                                 
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        if (str.substring(i-1, i).equals("x"))                                                              if (str.substring(i-1, i).equals("x"))                                                      
            {                                                                                                   {                                                                                       
                 index1= i;                                                                                          index1= i;                                                                         
            	break;                                                                                             	break;                                                                                 
             }                                                                                                   }                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    for(int i=str.length();i>0;i--)                                                                     for(int i=str.length();i>0;i--)                                                                 
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        if (str.substring(i-1, i).equals("y"))                                                              if (str.substring(i-1, i).equals("y"))                                                      
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            index2= i;                                                                                          index2= i;                                                                              
            break;                                                                                              break;                                                                                  
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return index1<index2;                                                                               return index1<=index2;                                                                          
}                                                                                                   }

public boolean in1To10(int n, boolean outsideMode)                                                  public boolean in1To10(int n, boolean outsideMode)                                                  
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (!outsideMode);                                                                                  if (!outsideMode);                                                                              
        if ( n > 0 && n < 11)                                                                               if ( n > 0 && n < 11)                                                                       
            return true;                                                                                        return true;                                                                            
    if (outsideMode)                                                                                    if (outsideMode)                                                                                
        if (n <= 1)                                                                                         if (n <= 1)                                                                                 
            return true;                                                                                        return true;                                                                            
    	else if ( n >= 10)                                                                                 	if ( n >= 10)                                                                                  
            return true;                                                                                        return true;                                                                            
    return false;                                                                                       return false;                                                                                   
}                                                                                                   }

public String zipZap(String str)                                                                    public String zipZap(String str)                                                                    
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    String newStr = "";                                                                                 String newStr = "";                                                                             
    int i = 0;                                                                                          int i = 0;                                                                                      
    while(i < str.length()-2)                                                                           while(i < str.length())                                                                         
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        String strA = Character.toString(str.charAt(i));                                                    String strA = Character.toString(str.charAt(i));                                            
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
        if ((str.charAt(i) == 'z') && (str.charAt(i+2) == 'p'))                                             if ((str.charAt(i) == 'z') && (str.charAt(i+2) == 'p') && (i < str.length()-2))             
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            newStr = newStr.concat(strA);                                                                       newStr = newStr.concat("zp");                                                           
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
            i = i+2;                                                                                            i = i+3;                                                                                
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        else                                                                                                else                                                                                        
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            newStr = newStr.concat(strA);                                                                       newStr = newStr.concat(strA);                                                           
            i++;                                                                                                i++;                                                                                    
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    newStr = newStr.concat("p");                                                                        newStr = newStr.concat("p");                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    return newStr;                                                                                      return newStr;                                                                                  
}                                                                                                   }

{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    for (int i = 0; i <= nums.length - 1; i++) {                                                        for (int i = 0; i <= nums.length - 2; i++) {                                                    
        if (nums[i] != val && nums[i+1] != val) {                                                           if (nums[i] != val && nums[i+1] != val) {                                                   
            return false;                                                                                       return false;                                                                           
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return true;                                                                                        return true;                                                                                    
}                                                                                                   }

public boolean endOther(String a, String b)                                                         public boolean endOther(String a, String b)                                                         
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	String aa = a.toLowerCase();                                                                       	String aa = a.toLowerCase();                                                                       
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	String bb = b.toLowerCase();                                                                       	String bb = b.toLowerCase();                                                                       
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	int aL = a.length();                                                                               	int aL = a.length();                                                                               
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	int bL = b.length();                                                                               	int bL = b.length();                                                                               
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	String bb = b.substring(bL, aL);                                                                   	String bb = b.substring(bL, aL);                                                                   
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	return (aa.endsWith(bb));                                                                          	return (aa.equals(bb));                                                                            
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
}                                                                                                   }

public boolean evenlySpaced(int a, int b, int c)                                                    public boolean evenlySpaced(int a, int b, int c)                                                    
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int evenlySpaced;                                                                                   int evenlySpaced;                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    if (a > b)                                                                                          if (a > b)                                                                                      
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	evenlySpaced = b;                                                                                  	evenlySpaced = b;                                                                             
        b = a;                                                                                              b = a;                                                                                      
        a = evenlySpaced;                                                                                   a = evenlySpaced;                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    else if (b > c)                                                                                     else if (b > c)                                                                                 
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	evenlySpaced = c;                                                                                  	evenlySpaced = c;                                                                             
        c = b;                                                                                              c = b;                                                                                      
        b = evenlySpaced;                                                                                   b = evenlySpaced;                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    else if (c > a)                                                                                     else if (c > a)                                                                                 
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	evenlySpaced = a;                                                                                  	evenlySpaced = a;                                                                             
        a = c;                                                                                              a = c;                                                                                      
        c = evenlySpaced;                                                                                   c = evenlySpaced;                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    return (a - b == c - b);                                                                            return (a - b == b - c);                                                                        
}                                                                                                   }

    		if (str.indexOf(y) > x)                                                                           	for (int lookY = str.indexOf(x); lookY < str.length(); 			lookY++)

                return true;                                                                                    char y = str.charAt(lookY);

    		else if (x > str.indexOf(y))                                                                              {

public boolean canBalance(int[] nums)                                                               public boolean canBalance(int[] nums)                                                               
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int sum = 0;                                                                                        int sum = 0;                                                                                    
    for (int num: nums)                                                                                 for (int num: nums)                                                                             
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        sum = sum + num;                                                                                    sum = sum + num;                                                                            
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    int half = sum/2;                                                                                   int half = sum/2;                                                                               
    sum = 0;                                                                                            sum = 0;                                                                                        
    for (int num: nums)                                                                                 int secondSum = 0;                                                                              
    {                                                                                                   for (int num: nums)                                                                             
        sum = sum + num;                                                                                {                                                                                               
        if (sum == half)                                                                                                                                                                                
        {                                                                                                   if (sum != half)                                                                            
            return true;                                                                                    {                                                                                           
        }                                                                                                       sum = sum + num;                                                                        
    }                                                                                                       }                                                                                           
                                                                                                            else                                                                                        
    return false;                                                                                           {                                                                                           
                                                                                                                secondSum = secondSum + num;                                                            
}                                                                                                           }                                                                                           
                                                                                                        }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                        return secondSum == half;                                                                       
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                    }

public boolean evenlySpaced(int a, int b, int c)                                                    public boolean evenlySpaced(int a, int b, int c)                                                    
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int num;                                                                                            int num;                                                                                        
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    if (a > b)                                                                                          if (a > b)                                                                                      
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	num = b;                                                                                           	num = b;                                                                                      
        b = a;                                                                                              b = a;                                                                                      
        a = num;                                                                                            a = num;                                                                                    
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    else if (b > c)                                                                                     else if (c > b)                                                                                 
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	num = c;                                                                                           	num = b;                                                                                      
        c = b;                                                                                              b = c;                                                                                      
        b = num;                                                                                            c = num;                                                                                    
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    else if (c > a)                                                                                     else if (c > a)                                                                                 
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	num = a;                                                                                           	num = a;                                                                                      
        a = c;                                                                                              a = c;                                                                                      
        c = num;                                                                                            c = num;                                                                                    
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    return (a - b == b - c);                                                                            return (a - b == b - c);                                                                        
}                                                                                                   }

public int caughtSpeeding(int speed, boolean isBirthday)                                            public int caughtSpeeding(int speed, boolean isBirthday)                                            
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (isBirthday == true)                                                                             if (isBirthday == true)                                                                         
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        speed = speed + 5;                                                                                  speed = speed - 5;                                                                          
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    if (speed >= 81)                                                                                    if (speed >= 81)                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return 2;                                                                                           return 2;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (speed < 81 && speed >= 61)                                                                 else if (speed < 81 && speed >= 61)                                                             
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return 1;                                                                                           return 1;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return 0;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
}                                                                                                   }

	{                                                                                                  	{

		return 2;                                                                                         		return 2;                                                                                         
		                                                                                                  		                                                                                                  
	}                                                                                                  	}                                                                                                  
	                                                                                                   	                                                                                                   
	else if (speed < 81 && speed >= 61)                                                                	else if (speed < 81 && speed >= 61)

    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return true;                                                                                        return true;                                                                                
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else if (isMorning == true)                                                                     
    {                                                                                                   {

    }                                                                                                   }

                                                                                                        {                                                                                               
                                                                                                            return true;
